                  "LanguageCode": "en",
                  "Value": "ISO symbol, In the case of sensory disorders of the skin, circulatory and lymphatic drainage disorders as well as skin formations consult a doctor before use. Do not use the knee ligament in combination with other compression products, creams, skin oils, etc. In the event of tingling or numbness during the use, or white or violet colouring of the skin, remove the bandage immediately and check whether the correct size bandage is worn. Do not wear while sleeping or during longer rest periods. Stop using in case skin irritations occur and consult a doctor if the symptoms persists. Discontinue use if if the elasticity of the bandage decreases. Keep out of reach of children. Inform the manufacturer and the relevant authorities about any serious incidents. Store in the original packaging, which contains important information."
